name: Underwater alien from planet Gliese 1214 b
description: This alien comes from the planet Gliese 1214 b, is an exoplanet that orbits the star Gliese 1214, Its parent star is 48 light-years from the Sun, in the constellation Ophiuchus. This species lives both under water and on the frozen surface. This illustration has been created by hand in procreate.artist: Pol Verdeguer Twitter: @polveiga Instagram: Polvvdraw
